    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>掌控加密货币挖矿的人——掌控世界。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>只有两个真正的硬汉能阻止这场疯狂——残暴约翰和他的伙伴，残暴狗。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859620/extras/e37a974ca3d6a3932a4ae5df74c9515d.poster.avif?t=1772204475\" width=608 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859620/extras/e37a974ca3d6a3932a4ae5df74c9515d.webm?t=1772204475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859620/extras/e37a974ca3d6a3932a4ae5df74c9515d.mp4?t=1772204475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验《残暴约翰2》，这是一场融合了《毁灭公爵》《英雄萨姆》《毁灭战士》和《半条命》等经典老派FPS游戏精髓的震撼之旅。沉浸于一场令人心跳加速的极度暴力游戏体验中，尽情释放你的肾上腺素。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859620/extras/5ea8d2139d586b63ca8c9f50e3c0a37e.poster.avif?t=1772204475\" width=608 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859620/extras/5ea8d2139d586b63ca8c9f50e3c0a37e.webm?t=1772204475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859620/extras/5ea8d2139d586b63ca8c9f50e3c0a37e.mp4?t=1772204475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于游戏：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>准备迎接2090年的一场震撼冒险吧！整个世界都被冷酷无情的加密货币挖矿变种人卢兹利安所控制。人类的命运掌握在他贪婪而残忍的手中，全球经济陷入崩溃，地球岌岌可危。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859620/extras/4753dd2c1d1ed1dcb5366f067ab45d1d.poster.avif?t=1772204475\" width=608 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859620/extras/4753dd2c1d1ed1dcb5366f067ab45d1d.webm?t=1772204475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859620/extras/4753dd2c1d1ed1dcb5366f067ab45d1d.mp4?t=1772204475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>疯狂剧情：拯救世界于加密挖矿的疯狂之中。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真正的老派FPS，拥有复古风格的画面与玩法，致敬90年代的传奇射击游戏。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扮演残暴约翰和他忠诚的伙伴残暴狗，各自拥有独特的关卡剧情。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>使用毁灭性的武器库，体验超细致爆裂系统，每一发子弹都将敌人撕碎成血肉横飞。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>史诗级Boss战：挑战巨型脑机和恐怖外星霸主。</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索宇宙：在整个游戏中发现秘密和彩蛋。</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索精彩场景：科幻太空站、城市、西部荒野、洞穴、赌场、加密矿厂等等。</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卓越的动态变化老派原声音乐。</strong></p></li></ul>",
